description:
Demi Moore [Ghost, G.I. Jane, Indecent Proposal, A Few Good Men, Striptease, Charlie’s Angels] and writer/director Shana Feste [The Greatest, Country Strong, Endless Love], talk with Anna about female sexuality, orgasms, marriage, fantasy role-playing, their new erotic podcast, Dirty Diana and more. Then Anna is joined by author and Clinical Director of the Center for Healthy Sex in Los Angeles, Dr. Alex Katehakis to give some qualified and unqualified advice to Amber.
